Package sudoku

package sudoku
  • Class
    Description
    AppFrame
    This is the JFrame initializer class.
    ButtonInitializer
    This class initializes the NumberButtons in a 9x9 pattern to a JPanel.
    ChangeListener
    A listener class for NumberButton to detect when a button is active and get the user input.
    Game
    This class generates a game with Generator into a Grid and also makes a ButtonInitializer to make the game visible.
    GameDialog
    This class is a JDialog for the beginning dialog or when starting a new game with the option to change the hardness.
    Generator
    A Generator to generate random Sudoku Grid instances.
    Grid
    This class represents a Sudoku Grid consisting of a 9x9 matrix containing nine 3x3 sub-grids of Grid.Cells.
    Grid.Cell
    This class represents a Cell within a Sudoku Grid.
    Main
     
    NewGame
     
    NumberButton
    This class represents a single JButton with a number on it which is determined by the Grid.Cells value that is in the same NumberButton.row and NumberButton.column as the button.
    RecordsDialog
    This class stores and shows the RecordsDialog.Records.
    RecordsDialog.Record
     
    RoundButtonUI
    This class is an override of a BasicButtonUI to make a circle button with a custom RoundButtonUI.color.
    Solver
    A Solver is capable of solving a given Sudoku Grid.
